title: What Home Sellers Should Be Prepared For in A Changing Market
description: Join Redfin economist Daryl Fairweather and agents Kaptan Unugur, of Sotheby’s International Realty in New York, and Miltiadis Kastanis, of Douglas Elliman in Florida, for a discussion on how sellers can make the most of a changing market. Moderated by Mansion Global reporter Leslie Hendrickson.
